<template>
	<router-view />
</template>

<style>
	#app {
		font-family: Avenir, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
		-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
		text-align: center;
		color: #2c3e50;
	}

	#nav {
		padding: 30px;
	}

	#nav a {
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #2c3e50;
	}

	#nav a.router-link-exact-active {
		color: #42b983;
	}


	.header-title {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.header-owner {
		height: 140px;
		margin: 0px;
		margin-bottom: 1%;
	}

	.header-owner-info {
		margin-top: 0px;
		float: right;
		text-align: right;
	}

	.header-owner-icon {
		float: right;
		width: 180px;
		height: 19px;
	}

	.header-icon {
		text-align: left;
		width: 100px;
		height: 40px;
	}

	.header-hr {
		*margin: 0;
		color: #000000;
		background-color: #000000;
		height: 1px;
	}

	.header-timestamp {
		margin: 0px;
		text-align: right;
		font-size: 20px;
	}


	.header-outline {
		margin-top: 1%;
		margin-bottom: 5%;
		text-align: center;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 27px;
		margin-bottom: 1%;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-top: 0%;
		font-size: 22px;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	h3 {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	outline {
		margin: 10%;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px solid black;
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1%;
	}

	.right {
		position: absolute;
		padding: 3%;
		right: 0px;
	}

	.textleft {
		position: absolute;
		padding: 3%;
		right: 290px;
	}
</style>
